ive Investigation scores."},{"name":"Divine Smite","desc":"When you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, you can expend one spell slot to deal radiant damage to the target, in addition to the weapon’s damage. The extra damage is 2d8 for a 1st-level spell slot, plus 1d8 for each spell level higher than 1st, to a maximum of 5d8. The damage increases by 1d8 if the target is an undead or a fiend, to a maximum of 6d8."},{"name":"Divine Health","desc":"The divine magic flowing through you makes you immune to disease."},{"name":"Aura of Protection","desc":"Whenever you or a friendly creature within 10 feet of you must make a saving throw, the creature gains a +3 bonus to the saving throw. You must be conscious to grant this bonus."},{"name":"Channel Divinity","desc":"Abilities marked with Channel Divinity cost a Channel Divinity charge. A charge recharges on a short or long rest."},{"name":"Fey Ancestry","desc":"Captain Sabrina Liaro has advantage on saving throws against being charmed, and magic can't put her to sleep."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"Captain Sabrina Liaro is a 6-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC [CHA SAVE], [CHA ATK] to hit with spell attacks). She has the following 12 spells prepared:\n\n> Cantrips (at will): _Guidance, Mending_\n> 1st level (4 slots): _Command, Compelled Duel, Cure Wounds, Detect Evil and Good, Protection from Evil and Good_\n> 2nd level (2 slots): _Lesser Restoration, Protection from Poison, Warding Bond, Zone of Truth_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"Captain Sabrina Liaro makes two attacks."},{"name":"Longsword","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D8] slashing damage."},{"name":"Hand Crossbow","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, range 30/120 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] piercing damage."},{"name":"Divine Sense (4 / Long Rest)","desc":"You can open your awareness to detect presence of strong evil. Until the end 